This is an unofficial third-party Electron wrapper for the Proton Wallet
web app (https://wallet.proton.me). It is not endorsed by or affiliated
with Proton AG. "Proton" and "Proton Wallet" are trademarks of Proton AG.

This project bundles no Proton code or assets other than the icon in
icons/icon.png, which is a copy of Proton's own publicly served PWA icon
(https://wallet.proton.me/assets/android-chrome-512x512.png). It only
loads the Proton Wallet web app in an Electron window at runtime. Your
use of Proton Wallet remains subject to Proton's own Terms of Service.
